unit.doc: Package definitionThis module contains all the types used to build an OASIS package. A package is described by an '_oasis' file.Sylvain Le Gall

type.doc: Name of a package, see OASISTypespackage.
Package name for findlib, doesn't contain '.'.
Package name + path for findlib, made of several findlib name concatenated with '.'.

Anything else, follow URL for description.
